00:41:36,670 --> 00:41:39,770
Something that was out of my control.

456
00:41:39,770 --> 00:41:44,270
Because I was powerless, I couldn't do anything but suffer.

457
00:41:49,600 --> 00:41:51,630
What's the real reason you came to Korea?

